'''Taglisya''' tezmer ad tesεu anamek uzadaɣ ideg ttnejmaεen Imasiḥiyen akken ad ẓẓallen u ad εebden illu-nsen, neɣ kra n wegdud imasiḥiyen i yecrek yiwen webrid n weεbad, i tezdi dɣa yiwet n ṭṭayfa.

==Titimulujit==
Isem-is ad yili yusa-d si tegrigit : εκκλησια (iklisya) s unamek : anejmuε, ma mačči d ddeεwa, neɣ si tseryanit : ܟܢܫܐ s unamek n unjmeε, tarbaεt n medden. 

== Amezruy==
Amezruy n lebni n teglisyiwin yedda d temhazt ureṣṣi n tmasiḥit deg umaḍal aṛumani, deg Usammar neɣ anda nniḍen. Ixamen imezwura i tent-icuban ttwabnan ahat gar 233 d 256 sld Tal. Ma gar leqrun  11 d 14, llant-d tkatidraliyin deg Tuṛuft.
